                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9967" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2513</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1758 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自主创新与合作创新：阿维塔长期技术战略的下一步决策</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">R&amp;D Independent Innovation and Co-innovation: AVATR&#39;s Decision for Long-Term Technology Strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">何佳讯，邹玥，周雯欣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阿维塔科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阿维塔；智能电动汽车品牌；可持续竞争优势；创新生态系统；技术创新战略；2025百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">AVATR, Intelligent electric vehicle brand, Sustainable competitive  advantage, Innovation ecosystem, Technological innovation strategy </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阿维塔科技（以下简称阿维塔）叠加长安的全产业链、华为智能科技、宁德电池生态，创新性地打造了“1+1+1＞3”的产业协同模式，实现了三大产业巨头的优势倍增效应。这种深度融合的产业架构，使阿维塔在高端智能电动汽车赛道中占据独特的竞争优势。自2018年建立以来，阿维塔立足于长安汽车的智能制造底蕴、宁德时代的电池技术突破，融合了华为在智慧出行领域的前沿技术，构建了“新架构、强计算、高压充电”的全新一代智能电动汽车技术平台，取得了出色的技术和市场表现，成为高端智能电动汽车领域中一股强劲的新生力量。本案例介绍了阿维塔在创新生态系统中技术战略选择的过程，在此基础上聚焦于长远发展视角对下一步技术战略决策点展开讨论。以一手访谈资料为依据，描述了阿维塔在自主创新和合作创新过程中的现状和潜在挑战，引出对技术创新路径选择的讨论。通过对案例情节的回顾和思考，帮助学生深入理解和掌握相关理论知识，从企业可持续竞争优势构建的角度，引导学生从实践中理解如何制定长期技术战略及具体实施方案。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">AVATR has extended the Changan Whole Industry Chain, Huawei Intelligent Technology, and CATL Battery Ecology, innovatively creating a &quot;1+1+1&gt;3&quot; industrial synergy model, achieving a multiplier effect of the advantages of the three major industry giants. This deeply integrated industrial architecture gives AVATR a unique competitive advantage in the high-end smart electric vehicle market. Since its establishment in 2018, AVATR has been based on Changan Automobile&#39;s intelligent manufacturing foundation and CATL&#39;s battery technology breakthrough, integrating Huawei&#39;s cutting-edge technology in the field of smart travel, and building a new generation of smart electric vehicle technology platform with &quot;new architecture, powerful computing, and high-voltage charging&quot;, achieving excellent technical and market performance and becoming a strong new force in the high-end smart electric vehicle field. This case study introduces the process of AVATR&#39;s technology strategy selection in the innovation ecosystem, focusing on the discussion of the next step of technology strategy decision-making points for long-term development. Based on first-hand interview data, this case describes the current situation and challenges of AVATR brand in the process of independent innovation and co-innovation, and leads to a discussion on the selection of technological innovation paths. By reviewing and reflecting on the case plot, we aim to help students gain a deeper understanding and mastery of relevant theoretical knowledge. From the perspective of building sustainable competitive advantages for enterprises, we guide students to understand how to formulate long-term technology strategies and their implementation plans through practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《技术与创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌定位；品牌双元本性论；创新模式；平台型创新生态系统；自主创新；关键核心技术；企业的可持续竞争优势；创新生态系统的演化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
